OL,3,CWales becomes first nation in the UK
OL,4,Cto ban greyhound racing
OL,6,FGreyhound racing is to be made illegal
OL,7,Fin Wales.
OL,9,FMembers of the Senedd backed a bill on
OL,10,FTuesday 17 March to ban racing across
OL,11,Fthe country with supporters saying the
OL,12,Fdecision will protect the animals.
OL,14,FBut critics of the ban say they have
OL,15,Flaunched a legal challenge against the
OL,16,Fdecision.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/3
