OL,3,CWales becomes first nation in the UK
OL,4,Cto ban greyhound racing
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government says a transition
OL,7,Fperiod will be in place to allow the
OL,8,Findustry to 'wind down responsibility'
OL,9,Fand to strengthen rehoming
OL,10,Farrangements for retired greyhounds.
OL,12,FThey add that the prohibition of
OL,13,Fracing will come into effect between 1
OL,14,FApril 2027 and 1 April 2030.
OL,16,FHuw Irranca-Davies, Deputy First
OL,17,FMinister with responsibility for
OL,18,FClimate Change and Rural Affairs,
OL,19,Fsaid: "Wales is a progressive nation,
OL,20,Fcommitted to ethical standards and
OL,21,Fforward-thinking legislation.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/3
