OL,3,CWales becomes first nation in the UK
OL,4,Cto ban greyhound racing
OL,6,F"This Bill strengthens our reputation
OL,7,Fas a leader on animal welfare and
OL,8,Fdelivers the standards that the people
OL,9,Fof Wales rightly expect."
OL,11,FAround 35,000 people originally signed
OL,12,Fa petition calling for a ban to be
OL,13,Fintroduced in Wales.
